<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_471_r1l22"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / . Alſo wöllen wir ew etwen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_471_r1l24"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Rats <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>ſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒü den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_471_line_1573134119350_35">nu </ab></add> auf den dinſtag gen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_471_r1l25"><expan>Mergenth<ex>eim</ex></expan> / vnd <expan>bit<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr <expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> / ob ıht darein viel / daʒ <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_471_r1l26">tag abgieng / daʒ Jr vns das cʒevviſſen tün wöllet ſo Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_471_r1l27">cʒeitlıchſt mügt / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>vrba<ex>n</ex>ȷ</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_471" id="235r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
