</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, also wöllen wir
                        ew etwen <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> rats <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> czü den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<add>nu</add> auf den <app><note><q type="date">dinstag</q>31.05.1412</note></app> gen <expan>Mergenth<ex>eim</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>bit<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                            <expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>, ob iht darein viel, daz
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> tag abgieng, daz ir uns das cze wissen
                        tün wöllet, so ir czeitlichst mügt. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Urba<ex>n</ex>i.</expan></ab>
</div>
